                href="https://messari.io/protocol-explorer/all-protocols"
                target="_blank">ON-CHAIN DATA</a
              ></span
            >), INDEXING BLOCKCHAIN DATA FOR VARIOUS PROTOCOLS VIA STANDARDIZED
